{
  "levelId": "forest-05",
  "chapterId": "forest-05",
  "worldId": "forest",
  "title": "风铃瀑布：找回风铃",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "falls",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/forest/forest-05.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "瀑布的风铃突然不响了。小鱼说，它被风吹到了彩虹后面。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是风铃瀑布。我们先把“找回风铃”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "scan",
          "prompt": "找到藏在彩虹光里的风铃。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "寻找叮叮声",
              "feedback": "风铃在藤蔓后面，找到了！"
            },
            {
              "label": "跟着水雾走",
              "feedback": "水雾散开，露出一条彩虹小路。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，寻找叮叮声让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "听故事也要用耳朵观察，声音会告诉我们方向。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "hero",
          "forest_guide"
        ],
        "props": [
          "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/props/forest/forest-05.webp"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
